{
  "texts": [
    "For any x ∈ X, h(x) ⊆ X by persistence for X, so h(x) ∈ X.",
    "Thus, h[X] ⊆ X.",
    "Now suppose Y ∈ h[S] ∩ X.",
    "Since Y ∈ X, Y ⊆ X, and since Y ∈ h[S], there is a y ∈ S such that h(y) = Y.",
    "If y ̸ ∈ X, then by refinability for X there is a minimal point a ⊑ y such that a ̸ ∈ X, so h(y) ̸ ⊆ X, contradicting the fact from the previous sentence that h(y) = Y ⊆ X."
  ]
}